[%#
Variables passed in:

user              - The user that owns the mailbox that is nearing or at quota.
mail_account_list - The quota status of the mailbox. This can be 'full', 'critical', 'warn'.
sent_to_root      - A default boolean flag sent to all templates that indicates if the message was sent to 'root'

For more information about how to customize notification templates, read our documentation at https://go.cpanel.net/notificationtemplates

-%]

[%
    PROCESS "include/colors.tmpl";
    PROCESS "include/styles.tmpl";

    WRAPPER 'wrapper/main.html.tmpl';

    NOTICE.email_reason = CPANEL.locale.maketext('Mail account quota notification for “[_1]”.', NOTICE.user);

%]

<p>
    [%
        CPANEL.locale.maketext('The following users are near to or have exceeded their individual mail quota:');
        FOREACH email IN NOTICE.mail_account_list
    %]
        <ul>
            <li>[%- email -%]</li>
        </ul>
    [%
        END
    %]
</p>

[% END %]
